[% PROCESS header.tmpl title="Silver Lining Dashboard:  Manage account"  %]
[% PROCESS left.tmpl %]

<div id="center">
<div class="content">

<h2>[% PROCESS settings/nav.tmpl %] > Manage account '[% reg.account_id.name %]'</h2>
<hr class="sl_line">
<p style="text-align: left; padding-bottom: 5px; width: 600px;">
<h1>Manage Account '[% reg.account_id.name %]'</h1>
<br />


[% IF msg %]
<p><font color="red">[% msg %]</font></p>
<p><hr class="sl_line"></p>
[% END %]

<p><a href="[% base_uri %]/app/settings/account">Change Login Info</a></p>
[% IF reg.account_id.account_id == 1 or reg.account_id.account_id ==2 or reg.account_id.account_id == 21 %]
<p><a href="[% base_uri %]/app/settings/users">Users</a></p>
<p><a href="[% base_uri %]/app/settings/payment">Payment</a></p>
[% END %]

<p>Your current subscription rate: <strong><font color="black">$[% IF reg.account_id.plan == 'enterprise' %]249 (Enterprise)[% ELSIF reg.account_id.plan == 'premium' %]99 (Premium)[% ELSIF reg.account_id.plan == 'plus' %]24 (Plus)[% ELSIF reg.account_id.plan == 'basic' %]5 (Basic)[% ELSIF reg.account_id.plan == 'free' %]0 (Free)[% END %]</font></strong></p>
<p>To change your subscription plan, just <a href="http://www.silverliningnetworks.com/pricing/?email=[% reg.email %]">click here to view subscription plans</a> and use <strong><font color="black">[% reg.email %]</font></strong> when you select a different plan.</p>

<p>You can cancel at anytime.  To cancel your subscription, email <a href="mailto:support@silverliningnetworks.com">support@silverliningnetworks.com</a> and we will notify you promptly once your subscription is canceled.</p>


<p><hr class="sl_line"></p>

[% IF reg.root %]
<form method="POST" action="[% base_uri %]/app/settings/root">


<p>
<select name="account_id" id="account_id">

[% FOREACH account = accounts %]

<option value="[% account.account_id %]" [% IF reg.account_id.account_id == account.account_id %]SELECTED[% END %]>[% account.name %]</option>

[% END %]
</select>
&nbsp;
<input type="submit" value="Account">
</form>

</p>


<hr class="sl_line">

[% END %]



    </div>
</div>


[% PROCESS footer.tmpl %]

